{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxindeterminate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Indicator states","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"indeterminate","type":"text"}]},{"text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Particular cases","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Cases forbidden by design","level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Suggestions","level":2,"anchor":"Suggestions","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox\/b\/6578e5\/t\/3dd013a529"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Design documentation","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading"},{"text":"Orange","level":3,"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Business Tools","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identi